metadata.title: Forest, District and Management Area

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Boundaries; Forest, district, and management area boundaries described by coded forest number, management area number, ranger district codes, abbreviated district identifiers and administrative and management area boundary class. This coverage has both a Polygon Attribute Table and an Arc Attribute Table with accompanying attributes.
